  "body": "I have 4K screen with 250% scale factor set in display settings (Windows OS).\r\nThis makes the default window size to span beyond the desktop area. I had to resize the window (make it smaller) or maximize it.\r\nIn any case after I restart the app, it gets its initial size and centered position within the desktop.\r\nI think we need to persist in settings:\r\n- window state: Normal | Maximized\r\n- window geometry\r\n\r\nand restore these when launching the app.",
